desc: PickleUpper Pickleball Retriever Attaches to Pickleball Paddles and Makes it Easy to Pick Up Pickleballs without Bending Over. The Perfect Pickleball Accessory. Fits any Pickleball Paddle Handle. Simple to Use and Does Not Interfere with Play. Reduces Injuries and increases the fun. For All Skill Levels and All Ages.
